title: Tahir Muhedini
text: Tahir Muhedini is the honorary president of the <a href="Party%20for%20Justice%2C%20Integration%20and%20Unity">Party for Justice, Integration and Unity</a>. He won a <a href="Councillor">council</a> seat in the Municipality of <a href="Tirana">Tirana</a> as a result of the 2007 local elections.
